te-of-the-day-by-socrates-student-plato-one-of-the-penalties-for-refusing-to-participate-in-politics-is-a-powerful-warning-about-political-apathy-civic-responsibility-and-the-consequences-of-staying-silent/articleshow/132485171.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/quote-of-the-day-by-socrates-student-plato-one-of-the-penalties-for-refusing-to-participate-in-politics-is-a-powerful-warning-about-political-apathy-civic-responsibility-and-the-consequences-of-staying-silent/articleshow/132485171.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-07-18T23:33:12+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI World Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-132485266,imgsize-58596.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[Iran Supreme Leader's message to US: Mojtaba Khamenei calls Trump's signature worthless, issues new warning]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/132484102.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[Iran's Supreme Leader warned the United States of "unforgettable lessons" if attacks continued. He declared President Trump's signature "worthless and invalid" amid escalating conflict. Tehran suspended commitments under a recent interim agreement, citing US breaches. Both nations exchanged strikes on military and infrastructure targets. Regional security and global energy supplies remain a concern.]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/iran-supreme-leaders-message-to-us-mojtaba-khamenei-calls-trumps-signature-worthless-issues-new-warning/articleshow/132484102.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/iran-supreme-leaders-message-to-us-mojtaba-khamenei-calls-trumps-signature-worthless-issues-new-warning/articleshow/132484102.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-07-18T23:07:47+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmln