estroys-at-least-100-homes-triggers-mass-evacuation/articleshow/132481122.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-07-18T20:11:46+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI World Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-132482285,imgsize-1012085.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[Indian-origin woman jailed in UK for more than 2 years over Rs 2.8 crore Covid loan fraud]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/132482113.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/uk/indian-origin-woman-jailed-in-uk-for-more-than-2-years-over-rs-2-8-crore-covid-loan-fraud/articleshow/132482113.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/uk/indian-origin-woman-jailed-in-uk-for-more-than-2-years-over-rs-2-8-crore-covid-loan-fraud/articleshow/132482113.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-07-18T20:00:23+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI World Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-132482105,imgsize-1036466.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA['Blood for blood': Iran displays giant billboard with Donald, Melania and Trump children in coffins]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/132481537.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[A new billboard in Tehran shows Donald Trump and his family above coffins draped in the US flag. The prominent slogan 'Blood for Blood' signals Iran's intent for revenge against recent strikes. This display follows other murals targeting Trump, including one showing him in an open coffin. These actions occur as military tensions between Iran and the United States intensify.]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/blood-for-blood-iran-displays-giant-billboard-with-donald-melania-and-trump-children-in-coffins/articleshow/132481537.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/blood-for-blood-iran-displays-giant-billboard-with-donald-melania-and-trump-children-in-coffins/articleshow/132481537.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-07-18T19:49:15+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI World Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-132481939,imgsize-170227.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[Confusion, lack of equipment hindered Venezuela's response to earthquake that killed over 5,000: Report]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/132480638.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[Venezuelan military response to earthquakes faced significant delays. Poor coordination and delayed deployment orders slowed rescue efforts. Essential equipment shortages further hampered the armed forces' capabilities. Civilians and international teams performed initial rescue work. Economic crisis years eroded the military's operational readiness.]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/confusion-lack-of-equipment-hindered-venezuelas-earthquake-response-report/articleshow/132480638.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/confusion-lack-of-equipment-hindered-venezuelas-earthquake-response-report/articleshow/132480638.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-07-18T19:00:35+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI World Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-132481335,imgsize-1268372.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[US Air Force airman killed in heavy equipment accident at California space base ]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/132483631.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/23-year-old-us-air-force-airman-killed-in-heavy-equipment-accident-at-california-space-base/articleshow/132483631.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/23-year-old-us-air-force-airman-killed-in-heavy-equipment-accident-at-california-space-base/articleshow/132483631.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-07-18T22:28:32+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI World Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-132483683,imgsize-80262.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[Indian woman seeks help in getting F-1 visa appointment, Bill Ackman responds and receives massive backlash: 'Why don't you finance a Harvard in Kerala']]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/132481735.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/indian-woman-seeks-help-in-getting-f-1-visa-appointment-bill-ackman-responds-and-receives-massive-backlash-why-dont-you-finance-a-harvard-in-kerala/articleshow/132481735.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/indian-woman-seeks-help-in-getting-f-1-visa-appointment-bill-ackman-responds-and-receives-massive-backlash-why-dont-you-finance-a-harvard-in-kerala/articleshow/132481735.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-07-18T19:34:19+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI World Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-132481747,imgsize-173662.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[Famous chimpanzees solved puzzles that changed how humans understood intelligence, but their move to Berlin had a tragic ending]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/132481047.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[Pioneering chimpanzee experiments revealed advanced intelligence and problem-solving skills.  These apes demonstrated insight, challenging human uniqueness in reasoning.  After their research, the chimpanzees faced harsh conditions in Berlin.  Their welfare declined, and their lives were largely overlooked by history.  New research highlights their forgotten stories and ethical responsibilities in science.]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/science/famous-chimpanzees-solved-puzzles-that-changed-how-humans-understood-intelligence-but-their-move-to-berlin-had-a-tragic-ending/articleshow/132481047.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/science/famous-chimpanzees-solved-puzzles-that-changed-how-humans-understood-intelligence-but-their-move-to-berlin-had-a-tragic-ending/articleshow/132481047.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-07-18T19:03:31+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI Science Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-132481271,imgsize-155426.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA['Find this white man ... ': Canadian journalist receives death threat from Indian-origin for Sikh man's kirpan gym dispute video]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/132479423.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/find-this-white-man-canadian-journalist-receives-death-threat-from-indian-origin-for-sikh-mans-kirpan-gym-dispute-video/articleshow/132479423.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/find-this-white-man-canadian-journalist-receives-death-threat-from-indian-origin-for-sikh-mans-kirpan-gym-dispute-video/articleshow/132479423.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-07-18T18:52:10+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI World Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-132480635,imgsize-821092.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[Ludwig’s Streamer Games 2026: Event dates, livestream, venue, tickets, and creator lineup]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/132478708.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[Streamer Games 2026 is set to ignite the screens on August 1 and 2, hosted at the University of Southern California. Viewers can catch all the thrilling competitions live on platforms like YouTube and Twitch. With an impressive lineup of popular creators confirmed to participate, fans can find tickets and additional information on the official Streamer Games website.]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us-streamers/ludwigs-streamer-games-2026-event-dates-livestream-venue-tickets-and-creator-lineup/articleshow/132478708.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us-streamers/ludwigs-streamer-games-2026-event-dates-livestream-venue-tickets-and-creator-lineup/articleshow/132478708.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-07-18T16:43:22+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">Sumit Roy</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-132478708,imgsize-144444.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[Streamer University 2026 ending date explained as Kai Cenat reveals what happens before July 20]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/132479648.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[The grand finale of Streamer University 2026, hosted by Kai Cenat, is set for July 20th morning. Alumni have begun to flock to campus to engage with students in these last days of festivities. Kai has made it clear that any rule infractions could lead to expulsion from campus. This year's event boasts a longer duration than its predecessor, designed to maximize creative collaboration and ensure a vibrant atmosphere.]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us-streamers/streamer-university-2026-ending-date-explained-as-kai-cenat-reveals-what-happens-before-july-20/articleshow/132479648.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us-streamers/streamer-university-2026-ending-date-explained-as-kai-cenat-reveals-what-happens-before-july-20/articleshow/132479648.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-07-18T17:33:22+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">Sumit Roy</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-132479772,imgsize-13914.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[Why was Ice Poseidon’s Indian VISA revoked? Streamer says it was linked to fellow Kick creator]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/132479941.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[Kick streamer Ice Poseidon's planned India trip was cancelled after his visa was revoked.  He learned his visa was denied due to his contact, Deepak, who has alleged criminal issues.  Authorities reportedly stated they would not accept him into India based on Deepak's information.  Deepak was allegedly involved in a fireworks incident where a girl was injured.  Ice Poseidon presented this gathered information as his reason for denial.]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us-streamers/why-was-ice-poseidons-indian-visa-revoked-streamer-claims-revoked-visa-was-linked-to-fellow-kick-creator/articleshow/132479941.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us-streamers/why-was-ice-poseidons-indian-visa-revoked-streamer-claims-revoked-visa-was-linked-to-fellow-kick-creator/articleshow/132479941.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-07-18T17:55:04+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">Sumit Roy</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-132480070,imgsize-329730.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA['Lot of confusion and misinformation': PhD supervisor of Kimi K3 CEO breaks silence on why Zhilin Yang did not stay in US]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/132480300.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/lot-of-confusion-and-misinformation-phd-supervisor-of-kimi-k3-ceo-breaks-silence-on-why-zhilin-yang-did-not-stay-in-us/articleshow/132480300.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/lot-of-confusion-and-misinformation-phd-supervisor-of-kimi-k3-ceo-breaks-silence-on-why-zhilin-yang-did-not-stay-in-us/articleshow/132480300.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-07-18T18:01:40+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI World Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-132480362,imgsize-35674.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA['Everyone I root for has lost': NYC Mayor Zohran Mamdani on FIFA World Cup final favourite]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/132477922.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/everyone-i-root-for-has-lost-nyc-mayor-zohran-mamdani-on-fifa-world-cup-final-favourite/articleshow/132477922.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/everyone-i-root-for-